{"tid":1715520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔屌唔鬆化】教育局宣布全港學校明日停課","createTime":"2019-11-13T06:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T06:56:20.000Z","uid":156363,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3b5e414c8e6d4884fec4fafd978e0a46b241ce21","tid":1715520,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:16:36.000Z","msg":"777個腦真係裝屎，山竹係咁今次又係咁，八仔都唔識用既特首點會體恤民情架。"},{"pid":"ceb228706ddc94f9cf2b901658d8fb24187a49a8","tid":1715520,"uid":42662,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:16:58.000Z","msg":"中圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0819f7f26a7aef90f4c68e94860b1f084f74d163","tid":1715520,"uid":198783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:17:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491862-20191113.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491862-20191113.htm&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=a2113231\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491862-20191113.htm&h=9090b319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491862-20191113.htm</a>"},{"pid":"98dc9d14c7dcbc9e1bd1918571b2afa9deb889b0","tid":1715520,"uid":266741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b5e414c8e6d4884fec4fafd978e0a46b241ce21","tid":1715520,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:16:36.000Z","msg":"777個腦真係裝屎，山竹係咁今次又係咁，八仔都唔識用既特首點會體恤民情架。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:17:19.000Z","msg":"因為佢根本唔係為市民服務，只考慮權貴上級需要"},{"pid":"f4644ce2ef772e1cec1b20f7651779ff3b9ea7db","tid":1715520,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:17:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/13/P2019111300500.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201911%2F13%2FP2019111300500.htm&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=83c2b73c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/13/P2019111300500.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n教育局特別宣布（二）<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  因應當前及可預計的交通狀況，以及全港學校的整體匯報，全港學校（包括幼稚園、小學、中學及特殊學校）<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">將於明日（十一月十四日）停課，以策安全。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n  教育局發言人今日（十一月十三日）表示，局方一直以學生的安全及福祉為首要考慮。在停課期間，各學校必須保持校舍開放，並安排教職員在安全情況下回校照顧學生，如果家長有需要送子女返回學校，可繼續送子女返校，並在途中注意安全，以及與學校保持溝通。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人續說，社會連日受到暴力示威者廣泛破壞，除製造危險的路面情況外，更有保姆車遭受惡意破壞，亦有學校遭受不同程度的威嚇，情況令人齒冷。教育局強烈譴責此等故意危害學童安全、剝奪學生學習基本權利的行為。<br />\n<br />\n  教育局強烈呼籲示威者立即停止所有暴力行為，盡快令社會回復秩序，讓學童安全上學。對於有教師工會不但不譴責暴力示威者，甚至將責任只推卸給警方，教育局認為有關言論實在有違教育工作者應有的專業態度。<br />\n<br />\n  教育局再次呼籲，學童留在家中，不要在街上流連，遠離危險，更切勿參加違法活動。<br />\n<br />\n  教育局會繼續跟進明日及往後的最新發展，適時為學校提供進一步指引及支援。局方再次感謝所有緊守崗位的教育工作者。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年11月13日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間14時10分"},{"pid":"0b91fd077a9313efcb85dda9ba28566995a39929","tid":1715520,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:17:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6efa98447625b130935cdef6e7be6cf17fc17573","tid":1715520,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceb228706ddc94f9cf2b901658d8fb24187a49a8","tid":1715520,"uid":42662,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:16:58.000Z","msg":"中圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:17:56.000Z","msg":"中計黨：中計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f18a2069b7460e90cf24bc663b20c7c8e0de5b","tid":1715520,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:17:59.000Z","msg":"明知係圈套都踩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ece3b4e38c0e6eebff26ad866bba5187cf1dea3","tid":1715520,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceb228706ddc94